Compliance Score: {{$json.compliance_score}}

ISSUES (must fix):
{{$json.issues.join('\n') || 'None'}}

WARNINGS (should fix):
{{$json.warnings.join('\n') || 'None'}}

PASSED:
{{$json.passed.join('\n') || 'None'}}

Provide:
1. Overall assessment (DEPLOY / FIX REQUIRED / CRITICAL BLOCK)
